{%- comment -%}
  Free shipping progress (spec §7: "hairline track, ink fill, '$22 away from
  free shipping' — turns Success with a check when reached"). A real,
  accessible <progress>-pattern meter (role="progressbar" with numeric ARIA,
  not just a colored div) computed entirely server-side from cart.total_price.
  Never recalculated in JS: this snippet lives inside the drawer/page's AJAX
  swap boundary (see cart-drawer.liquid, main-cart.liquid), so every cart
  change already re-renders it fresh via Shopify's own `sections` param —
  one place that knows the free-shipping math, not two.

  Gated on settings.cart_free_shipping_enabled + a merchant-set threshold —
  reads cart.total_price directly rather than checking real shipping rates
  (spec's own words: "messaging," not a shipping-rate calculator; the
  storefront has no access to computed rates before the shipping-info step
  anyway).
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if settings.cart_free_shipping_enabled -%}
  {%- liquid
    assign threshold = settings.cart_free_shipping_threshold | times: 100
    assign remaining = threshold | minus: cart.total_price
    assign progress = cart.total_price | times: 100.0 | divided_by: threshold | round
    if progress > 100
      assign progress = 100
    endif
    assign is_met = false
    if remaining <= 0
      assign is_met = true
    endif
    assign remaining_money = remaining | money
  -%}
  <div class="free-shipping-bar{% if is_met %} free-shipping-bar--met{% endif %}">
    <p class="free-shipping-bar__message">
      {%- if is_met -%}
        {% render 'icon', name: 'check', size: 14 %} {{ 'cart.free_shipping_met' | t }}
      {%- else -%}
        {{ 'cart.free_shipping_remaining' | t: amount: remaining_money }}
      {%- endif -%}
    </p>
    <div
      class="free-shipping-bar__track"
      role="progressbar"
      aria-valuenow="{{ progress }}"
      aria-valuemin="0"
      aria-valuemax="100"
      aria-label="{{ 'cart.free_shipping_progress_label' | t }}"
    >
      <div class="free-shipping-bar__fill" style="width: {{ progress }}%;"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
{%- endif -%}
